The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Aloke confident

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: The Bengal squad for the Santosh Trophy was announced on Sunday. Coach Aloke Mukherjee said: The boys are in good shape. I am planning to play in 4-4-2 format. 

The SQUAD: Goalkeepers: Rajat Ghosh Dastidar, Kalyan Chowbey, Subrata Pal; Defenders: Shankar Roy Choudhuri, Madhab Das, Saumik Dey, Shubash Chakraborty, Covan Lawrence, Amulya Mondal, Manas Das, Rajiv Ahmed; Midfielders: Chandan Das (vice-captain), Mehtab Hossain, Shashti Duley, Noel Wilson, Jayanta Sen; Forwards: Bhaichung Bhutia (captain), Rahim Nabi, Raman Vijayan, Dipendu Biswas. Coach: Aloke Mukherjee. 




